Type: Package
Package: covidPlots
Title: This package gives an overview of the covid-19 situation in the world.
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Ali",
           family = "Malek",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "ali.malek@ut.ac.ir",
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: This package uses the data operated by the Johns Hopkins University Center for Systems Science 
    and Engineering (JHU CSSE) to show a table of the total cases, deaths, and recovers and also 
    uses that data to plot a world map which is colored by the type of data chosen by the user 
    and time series for the country chosen by the user.
URL: https://github.com/Iarima/covidPlots
BugReports: https://github.com/Iarima/covidPlots/issues
